query:
SELECT e.id, e.name, e.profileImage, e.userId, u.name as userName, u.openId 
FROM employees e 
JOIN users u ON e.userId = u.id 
WHERE u.openId = 'manus|just2vip@gmail.com' OR u.email = 'just2vip@gmail.com';
